<h1>Privacy</h1>
<p>'afterwriting is a font-end only, open-source application. Your screenplay is not sent out unless you use Dropbox / Google Drive integration (then your screenplay is sent over SSL connection). PDF is generated inside the browser which means you can go offline and still write your screenplay!</p>
<p>The main reason behind it is to make sure the application can be run anytime, anywhere, even if you have no Internet connection. You can download <a href="afterwriting.zip" id="download-link">afterwriting.zip</a> file which contains the whole website. I recommend you to do it even if you are "always online" in case the website is down* or you forget to pay the pill. </p><p>(*) 'afterwriting is hosted on <a href="https://pages.github.com/">GitHub Pages</a> which is available 99% of the time. However according to Murphy's law "if a website is available 99% of the time, you will critically need to use during the other 1%", so... get a backup today! </p>
